        <h3>Our Manifesto</h3>
        <p>At Aks Skills Academy, we believe in the power of coding to transform lives. Our manifesto encapsulates our commitment to providing accessible, engaging, and high-quality coding education to children:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Empowerment:</strong> We empower students by equipping them with essential digital skills that prepare them for the future.</li>
            <li><strong>Creativity:</strong> We foster a creative environment where students can innovate and express their ideas through coding.</li>
            <li><strong>Engagement:</strong> Our courses are designed to be fun, interactive, and engaging, ensuring students enjoy the learning process.</li>
            <li><strong>Inclusivity:</strong> We welcome students of all backgrounds and abilities, making coding accessible to everyone.</li>
            <li><strong>Continuous Learning:</strong> We promote a culture of lifelong learning, encouraging students to explore and expand their knowledge beyond the classroom.</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Together, we aim to cultivate a generation of thinkers, creators, and leaders who will shape the digital world of tomorrow.</p>
